   <body>
      <p>This feature enables you to add a new scope.</p>
      <p>To add a new scope, please perform the following steps:</p>
      <ol>
         <li>Click Add New on the Scope page.<fig>
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432694/102432756.jpg"/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li>Select the required options from the Field, Operator, and Value drop-down lists.<fig>
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432694/102432755.jpg"/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li>Click Add Row to add extra rows.</li>
         <li>Click Save to save the changes.</li>
         <li>Click Cancel to start fresh.</li>
      </ol>
